{"title":"麦收小曲","authors":["巴牧"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":6,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦收小曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴牧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他把珍珠向蓝天抛洒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热风吹走缕缕灰沙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，满场金色的麦垛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遮住了几片云霞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"场院里是谁哼着小曲？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人在夸刚收下的庄稼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脱谷机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一条性烈的牲口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在场上发出怒吼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张嘴能吃千捆粮草。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霎时吐出金珠万斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子们拍手称赞："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这是不喝水的牯牛……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有它参加社里麦收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食入库不用发愁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"套马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"派出刚制的新车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"套上棕色的骏马。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭一根细长的竹鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快马能驰骋天下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶车人那有闲情玩耍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正把一车新粮交给国家。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}